Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting pretty chilly, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not too friendly today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just get off work, Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the restaurants in this area are already closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the hotel, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who live on this street...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for some reason, they all know me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,called me "Anna."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:10.63,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,218)\pos(364,357)}Door to a Nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Suk, a suspected serial\Nkiller, is hospitalized here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there aren't any police officers or patrol cars around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, there's no point unless I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sign of police anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A patient named Suk should be registered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan-Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were a number of casualties from\Nan abandoned building on Brno Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the one where a bunch of unemployed\Nmen got into a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:03:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unemployed men?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't understand what they said on the news, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that must be their cover story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, which rooms are they in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were seriously wounded, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they were all transferred out after receiving treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transferred?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ambulance came and took all six of them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six men attacked us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Detective Jan Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any patients who were\Nadmitted with gunshot wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no record of an emergency patient\Nnamed Jan Suk being brought here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Research documents and a tape\Npertaining to Kinderheim 511...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Petrov, who was the former director of Kinderheim 511...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and operated an unauthorized orphanage in Prague...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,entrusted me with them right before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who exactly is after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I don't actually know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the former Czechoslovakia!! secret\Npolice definitely want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the documents and the tape right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have them on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're being held at a certain place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of them, Detective Suk was seriously injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and abducted from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what they'll do to Suk in order\Nto get their hands on what they want...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do those things say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The documents are full of research data with\Ntechnical terms along with a roster...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't take a good look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only listened to the tape briefly, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was recorded on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice of a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was probably interrogated after being drugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When asked for his name, he answered "Johan."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinderheim 511...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Research documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the tape right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's conduct business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for you to become\Nfurther involved in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also have something I'd like to ask the\Nformer Czechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:07:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the problem now is whether or not\Nthese people will actually talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt you're inviting us to dinner, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's a bigshot in the former\NCzechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I looked them up at the newspaper agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Colonel Karel Ranke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the top man decided to come himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies for my subordinates\Ntreating you so roughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to a miscommunication in our command structure,\Nwe have an unexpected situation on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are currently suffering from\Na serious misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By you, and by society.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if we're a group of killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been placed in a hospital where we have connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has not been harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did not kill anyone in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that blonde girl acting on your orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do have reports about her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she has absolutely no ties with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are extremely inconvenienced by her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we want aren't human lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of mine in Germany wanted\Nthose documents and the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we had cautiously approached\NPetrov many times to negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then he was targeted and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there must've been lots of money involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is a business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to talk business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to have the documents\Nand the tape in exchange for Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's avoid such talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that must not be repeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something like that existed in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who knows what could happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that must never be repeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us put aside that sort of talk for now as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with this business negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm from that place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm from Kinderheim 511...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you leave there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, when I was fourteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was thirty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When were you put in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably when I was seven or eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around 1963, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know this child?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the early 60s...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was officially stationed in Berlin as an intelligence\Nofficer for the Czechoslovakian embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She married a German.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she and her husband tried to defect by crossing\Nthe Berlin Wall and they were shot to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And only that boy was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I signed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On paper, that place provided a wonderful environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ideal, educational environment\Nwhere children with a past...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be nurtured into the elites who would\Nshoulder the communism of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I signed the papers that allowed that child\Nto be placed in Kinderheim 511...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:10:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything that happened there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or from before I went there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know my real name...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to change something so horrible into money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're even trying to sell documents containing\Nexperimental data on your own nephew!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears we've gone off topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to think of this\Nas a beneficial business deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are free to go for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope for a positive answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them back with the utmost care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the most important thing is to rescue Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you agree to his demands...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he will release Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cocoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cocoa he had once a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looked forward to the weekly cocoa ration!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I had a fever and was lying in the infirmary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he brought me some cocoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His own cocoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he loved it so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never had such delicious cocoa before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to do something to repay him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said to remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, it was popular among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We talked about ourselves to our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't really understand it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but our memories were fading...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the strange classes we attended every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were even in danger of forgetting our own names...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we had our friends remember who we were!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He loved cocoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He loved to draw pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he loved insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he didn't like to collect insects because\Nhe had to kill them, and he didn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most fun he had was when he went\Ninto the forest with his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He caught lots of butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he released all the butterflies from\Nthe bug cage on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His dream was to become an entomologist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adolf Reinhart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't hide things from him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}can become anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cheers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, welcome back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, welcome back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, welcome back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The road leading to this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scenery...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This storefront signboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know this door, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know them, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought things over last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like you to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither those documents nor the tape\Nhave anything to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm also...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem like we have time to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they can't wait for more negotiating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The former Czechoslovakia^ secret police have\Nbothered to come all the way but here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to think things over?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of giving you either\Nthe tape or the research documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care what happens to Detective Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything were to happen to Suk...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the tape and research documents would be lost forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not start this kind of meaningless negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can let you listen to the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to forget your business deal with\Nyour German friend who's trying to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to listen to it because of a personal interest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'm willing to let you listen to the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}should{\i0} listen to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the sake of the nephew you\Nplaced in Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should listen to the voice of the boy named\NJohan who was recorded on the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not making any deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even as we speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone might be killed because of that tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many people involved with your\NCzechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you think have been killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think killed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the person who wants that tape the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The owner of the voice that was recorded on that tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've learned what that tape\Nis from your German friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he tell you to get?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The true identity of the monster..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was all he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to get you people involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll tell you everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before more people are killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Johan was tracing his own roots...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and came to Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be trying to erase everything, instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what did you people do fifteen years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a family living near Cedok\NBridge in the Michalska district.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, they were taken away by the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After taking him away from the building\Nwith the three frogs on its signboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what did you guys do to Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if being dragged down these stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that at the time, I was in a position\Nto receive all the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But these three frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a family being taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have absolutely no recollection of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pretend you don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, there was information that didn't reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the things that man did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know which division of the\Nsecret police he belonged to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor did I know whose command he was under.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, he could detain anyone\Nfreely without reporting to his superiors...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he was doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he was just a lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was given a luxurious mansion as his workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was known as the "Man of the Red Rose Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that man was involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a quiet man with an extremely elegant demeanor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't wear a uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and liked tea and cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was his name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:20:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz... Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I don't know if that was his real name or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since he also had a pen name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pen name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was also the author of a picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared of this door, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was reading a picture book in here, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone opened the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and came home...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a very peculiar picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The title was "The Monster Without\NA Name," or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this... memory...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have been reading a picture book in here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who opened the door and came in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm welcoming myself back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.85,0:22:31.02,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.02,0:22:44.45,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.02,0:22:44.45,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:47.41,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:23:01.09,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:23:01.09,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.69,0:23:25.95,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:34.37,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:36.83,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
